description: Redevelopment of site to provide a 8,292sq m multi purpose community sports centre and swimming pool, 902 sq m retail/commercial/restaurant/bar floorspace (use classes A1, A2, A3 and A4), 329 residential units and underground parking for 56 cars contained within a 43 storey tower measuring 144.3m in height and a part 7, part 8 storey block with roof terraces and courtyard.
